Ahead of the highly anticipated release of 20th Century Fox’s film, Deadpool 2 has joined forces with Omaze in the fight against cancer by putting up its pink suit for auction. The proceeds will go to Fuck Cancer, a non-profit organization interested in cancer, its prevention and providing support to cancer victims. Fundraisers will have the opportunity to win the pink suit  Deadpool 2 will be out in cinemas May 18.